```plantuml
@startuml sugarlabs_musicblocks-v4-lib

package "Syntax Representation" {
    [Element API] as ElementAPI
    [Specification] as Specification
    [Warehouse] as Warehouse
    [Syntax Tree] as SyntaxTree
}

package "Execution Engine" {
    [Symbol Table] as SymbolTable
    [Parser] as Parser
    [Interpreter] as Interpreter
    [Scheduler] as Scheduler
}

package "Library" {
    [Values] as Values
    [Boxes] as Boxes
    [Math Operators] as MathOps
    [Conditionals] as Conditionals
    [Loops] as Loops
    [Program Structures] as ProgramStructs
    [Miscellaneous] as Misc
}

ElementAPI --> Specification : defines
Specification --> Warehouse : manages
Warehouse --> SyntaxTree : creates instances for

SyntaxTree --> Parser : input
Parser --> Interpreter : parsed AST
Interpreter --> SymbolTable : accesses
Interpreter --> Scheduler : coordinates with

Library --> Specification : provides elements
Values --> Specification
Boxes --> Specification
MathOps --> Specification
Conditionals --> Specification
Loops --> Specification
ProgramStructs --> Specification
Misc --> Specification

@enduml
```